    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section id="faq" class="faq-block">
      <div class="faq-container">
        <h2 class="faq-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary><span>What is Aani and how does it work?</span><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></summary>
            <p>Aani transforms your audio recordings into high-quality, researched content. Simply record your thoughts, and our AI-augmented system—enhanced by human review—creates blogs, social posts, and more in your authentic voice.</p>
          </details>
          
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary><span>How is my privacy protected?</span><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></summary>
            <p>Your privacy is our top priority. All audio is encrypted in transit and at rest, stored on secure AWS servers, and automatically deleted within 7 days. We never sell your data or use it to train AI models. Read our full <a href="privacy.html">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
          </details>
          
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary><span>Where is my data stored and processed?</span><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></summary>
            <p>Your data is stored on secure AWS (Amazon Web Services) servers with enterprise-grade security. Processing happens in compliant data centers that meet international privacy standards including GDPR and APPP.</p>
          </details>
          
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary><span>How long do you keep my recordings?</span><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></summary>
            <p>Audio recordings are automatically deleted within 7 days. Processed content (transcripts and outputs) may be retained longer if you choose to save it, but you can request deletion at any time.</p>
          </details>
          
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary><span>What benefits do beta testers receive?</span><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></summary>
            <p>Beta testers receive exclusive lifetime benefits: a 30% discount on all future plans, early access to premium features, priority support, and direct input into product development.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-contact">
          <p>Have more questions? Email us at <a href="mailto:beta@aanihub.com">beta@aanihub.com</a></p>
